<text><body>
<lb n="0603a05" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0603a06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0603a07" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1146</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0603a08" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0603004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】久安四年寫東寺三蜜藏本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本，【丙】高山寺藏古寫本，【丁】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本</note>大虛空藏菩薩念誦法</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0603a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0603a10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0603005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】【甲】【丙】【丁】，（開府…寺）三十七字＝（唐）一字【明】【乙】</note><note n="0603005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺【大】，唐【明】【乙】，大興善寺【宋】【元】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603005"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0603a11" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0603a12" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">唐</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】【丙】【丁】">大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0603006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（大廣智）【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門【大】，門大廣智【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603006"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0603a13" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0603a14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0603a1401">我今依瑜伽金剛頂經。說寶部虛空藏菩薩
<lb n="0603a15" ed="T"/>真言教法。為愍念在家<note n="0603007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">山＝出【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">山【大】，出【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603007"><lem wit="【大】">山</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">出</rdg></app>家。薄福少德乏少
<lb n="0603a16" ed="T"/>資具者。所求世間出世間勝願多不遂意。若
<lb n="0603a17" ed="T"/>依此教法修行。業報等障皆悉消除。福德增
<lb n="0603a18" ed="T"/>長心神適悅。淨信大乘利樂有情。心無退轉。
<lb n="0603a19" ed="T"/><note n="0603008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＋（間）【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，世間【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603008"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">世間</rdg></app>出世間所有財寶悉皆獲得。於一切眾生
<lb n="0603a20" ed="T"/>能作利益。一稱一念所得福聚<note n="0603009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尚＝當【丁】</note><note n="0603009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尚【大】，當【丁】</note><app n="0603009"><lem wit="【大】">尚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">當</rdg></app>猶虛空。何
<lb n="0603a21" ed="T"/>況作意如法修<note n="0603010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＝持【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0603010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行【大】，持【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0603010"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">持</rdg></app>。所願必獲殊勝成就。行者
<lb n="0603a22" ed="T"/>先<note n="0603011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔應〕－【甲】</note><note n="0603011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0603011"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0603012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔入〕－【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0603012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】，〔－〕【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0603012"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>灌頂道場。親對師<note n="0603013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔前〕－【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前【大】，〔－〕【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603013"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>受得儀軌。或
<lb n="0603a23" ed="T"/>於山間靜處。或於寺舍隨所樂處。建立<note n="0603014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔精室〕－【丙】</note><note n="0603014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">精室【大】，〔－〕【丙】</note><app n="0603014"><lem wit="【大】">精室</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0603a24" ed="T"/>作一方壇。隨其大小。以瞿摩夷塗地。作八曼
<lb n="0603a25" ed="T"/><note n="0603015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝荼【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0603015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶【大】＊，荼【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0603015"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">荼</rdg></app>羅。周匝懸幡。上安天蓋。於壇西面安虛
<lb n="0603a26" ed="T"/>空藏菩薩像。持誦者壇東對像念誦。以種種
<lb n="0603a27" ed="T"/>時華散<note n="0603016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔於〕－【三】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603016"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>壇上。燒香燈明飲食菓子。隨力所
<lb n="0603a28" ed="T"/><note n="0603017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辦＝辨【宋】</note><note n="0603017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦【大】，辨【宋】</note><app n="0603017"><lem wit="【大】">辦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">辨</rdg></app>以為供養。每入道場。對尊像前五體投
<lb n="0603a29" ed="T"/>地。禮一切如來及諸聖眾。即懺悔隨喜勸請
<pb n="0603b" xml:id="T20.1146.0603b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0603b01" ed="T"/>發願已。然後結<note n="0603018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跏＝加【宋】【元】</note><note n="0603018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跏【大】，加【宋】【元】</note><app n="0603018"><lem wit="【大】">跏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">加</rdg></app>趺坐。或半<note n="0603019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跏＝加趺【宋】【元】，趺跏【明】【乙】，跏坐【丙】，跏＋（趺）【丁】</note><note n="0603019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跏【大】，加趺【宋】【元】，趺跏【明】【乙】，跏坐【丙】，跏趺【丁】</note><app n="0603019"><lem wit="【大】">跏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">加趺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">趺跏</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">跏坐</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">跏趺</rdg></app>隨意而坐
<lb n="0603b02" ed="T"/>端身正念。當以塗香<note n="0603020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔用〕－【丁】</note><note n="0603020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用【大】，〔－〕【丁】</note><app n="0603020"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>塗二手。虛心合掌如
<lb n="0603b03" ed="T"/><note n="0603021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未敷蓮花＝來敷花【丁】</note><note n="0603021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未敷蓮華【大】，來敷花【丁】</note><app n="0603021"><lem wit="【大】">未敷蓮華</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">來敷花</rdg></app>。誦清淨真言三遍或七遍頂上散
<lb n="0603b04" ed="T"/>印。則三業清淨以成勝義澡浴。淨三業真言
<lb n="0603b05" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0603b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b0601" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0603022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（一）夾註【丁】</note><note n="0603022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵【大】，唵(一)【丁】</note><app n="0603022"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>舜<note place="inline"><note n="0603023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">入＋（聲）【明】【乙】</note><note n="0603023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】，入聲【明】【乙】</note><app n="0603023"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">入聲</rdg></app></note>第耨戍<note place="inline">引</note>馱曩<note place="inline">引</note>耶娑囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0603024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0603024"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>賀<app type="star" corresp="#0603024"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0603b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b0701">次結佛部心三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0603b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b0801">以止觀十度。內相叉作拳。以禪智並竪。結印
<lb n="0603b09" ed="T"/>成已。觀想諸佛遍滿虛空。即誦佛部心真言
<lb n="0603b10" ed="T"/>三遍。頂上散印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0603b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b1101" cb:type="dharani">唵爾曩爾迦<note place="inline">半音</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<app type="star" corresp="#0603024"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0603b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b1201">次結蓮華部心三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0603b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b1301">準前佛部心印。智度屈入<note n="0603025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掌＋（中）【丙】</note><note n="0603025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">掌【大】，掌中【丙】</note><app n="0603025"><lem wit="【大】">掌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">掌中</rdg></app>。直竪禪度。結
<lb n="0603b14" ed="T"/>此契已。想於一切如來右邊。有觀自在菩薩
<lb n="0603b15" ed="T"/>并諸眷屬。<note n="0603026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即【三】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，即【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603026"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】">即</rdg></app>誦蓮華部心真言三遍。頂<note n="0603027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603027"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0603b16" ed="T"/>右散印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0603b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b1701" cb:type="dharani">唵阿<note place="inline"><note n="0603028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊，（引）【丁】</note><note n="0603028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】＊，去聲【明】【乙】＊，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->去引【丁】</note><app n="0603028"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">去聲</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">去引</rdg></app>引</note>嚧<note place="inline">引</note>力迦<note place="inline">半<note n="0603029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＋（呼）【三】【乙】＊，〔音〕－【丁】</note><note n="0603029" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->音【大】＊，音呼【宋】【元】【明】【乙】＊，〔－〕【丁】</note><app n="0603029"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">音呼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<app type="star" corresp="#0603024"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0603b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b1801">次結金剛部心三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0603b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b1901">准前佛部心印。以禪度屈入掌。直竪智度。想
<lb n="0603b20" ed="T"/>於一切如來左邊。有金剛手菩薩并諸眷屬。
<lb n="0603b21" ed="T"/>即誦金剛部心真言三遍。頂左散印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0603b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b2201" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<anchor xml:id="fxT20p0603b04"/><note place="inline">半音</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0603030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＋（引）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0603030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】，賀引【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0603030"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0603b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b2301">次結被甲護身印。</p>
<lb n="0603b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b2401">以觀羽禪度<note n="0603031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">橫＝撗【宋】【元】【丙】</note><note n="0603031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">橫【大】，撗【宋】【元】【丙】</note><app n="0603031"><lem wit="【大】">橫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【丙】">撗</rdg></app>於掌內。以進忍<note n="0603032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">戒檀＝檀戒【三】【乙】</note><note n="0603032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戒檀【大】，檀戒【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0603032"><lem wit="【大】">戒檀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">檀戒</rdg></app>四度。
<lb n="0603b25" ed="T"/>握拳結此契成印身五處所謂印額<note n="0603033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右肩左肩＝左右肩【丁】</note><note n="0603033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右肩左肩【大】，左右肩【丁】</note><app n="0603033"><lem wit="【大】">右<note n="0603034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">肩左＝右【甲】</note><note n="0603034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">肩左【大】，右【甲】</note><app n="0603034"><lem wit="【大】">肩左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">右</rdg></app>
<lb n="0603b26" ed="T"/>肩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">左右肩</rdg></app>心喉。是名五處護身真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0603b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b2701" cb:type="dharani">唵步<note place="inline">引</note>入嚩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0603035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【明】【乙】【丁】</note><note n="0603035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，囉【明】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0603035"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丁】">囉</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0603b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603b2801">由結此<note n="0603036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝耶【明】【乙】</note><note n="0603036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，耶【明】【乙】</note><app n="0603036"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">耶</rdg></app>加持五處。即成被金剛光焰堅固
<lb n="0603b29" ed="T"/>甲冑。一切諸魔不能障難。所持真言速得成
<pb n="0603c" xml:id="T20.1146.0603c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0603c01" ed="T"/>就。</p>
<lb n="0603c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603c0201">次<note n="0603037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔結〕－【甲】</note><note n="0603037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">結【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0603037"><lem wit="【大】">結</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>請虛空藏菩薩印。</p>
<lb n="0603c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603c0301">二羽金剛縛。直竪忍願。反蹙如寶形。進力各
<lb n="0603c04" ed="T"/>屈如鉤。想<note n="0603038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔於〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603038"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>壇中有寶樓閣。<note n="0603039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔於樓閣〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0603039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於樓閣【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0603039"><lem wit="【大】">於樓閣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內有
<lb n="0603c05" ed="T"/>八葉開敷蓮華。誦真言四遍。以進力向身招
<lb n="0603c06" ed="T"/>之。本尊并及眷屬皆來集會。迎請真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0603c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603c0701" cb:type="dharani">唵薩嚩怛他<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0603028"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">去聲</rdg></app></note>誐哆<note place="inline">引</note>毘<note n="0603040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囇＝曬【三】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0603040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囇【大】，曬【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0603040"><lem wit="【大】">囇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">曬</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>迦嚩日囉<note n="0603041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合囉〕－【三】【乙】</note><note n="0603041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合囉【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0603041"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二
<lb n="0603c08" ed="T"/>合</note>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>薩嚩<note place="inline">引</note>舍<note n="0603042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【丁】</note><note n="0603042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【丁】</note><app n="0603042"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>跛哩布囉迦弱吽
<lb n="0603c09" ed="T"/>鑁斛<note place="inline">引</note>怛囕<note n="0603043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合引〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0603043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合引【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0603043"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0603c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603c1001">次結軍<note n="0603044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吒＝荼【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0603044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吒【大】，荼【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0603044"><lem wit="【大】">吒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">荼</rdg></app>利身印。</p>
<lb n="0603c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603c1101">以檀慧右押左。相叉入掌。以戒方並押交上。
<lb n="0603c12" ed="T"/>以禪智並押戒方。以忍願直竪<note n="0603045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔頭〕－【甲】</note><note n="0603045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頭【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0603045"><lem wit="【大】">頭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>相拄。進力
<lb n="0603c13" ed="T"/>屈如鉤。作三<note n="0603046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝鈷【宋】</note><note n="0603046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">股【大】，鈷【宋】</note><app n="0603046"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">鈷</rdg></app>杵形。即誦軍吒利真言。隨
<lb n="0603c14" ed="T"/>誦以印。左旋三匝辟除一切諸魔。右轉三匝
<lb n="0603c15" ed="T"/>便成結界真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0603c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0603c1601" cb:type="dharani">曩謨囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>耶娜莫室戰<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0603c17" ed="T"/>合</note>拏摩賀嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>矩嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>馱<note place="inline">引</note>耶唵戶
<pb n="0604a" xml:id="T20.1146.0604a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0604a01" ed="T"/>魯戶魯底瑟<note n="0604001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">姹＝吒【甲】【丁】＊</note><note n="0604001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姹【大】＊，吒【甲】【丁】＊</note><app n="0604001"><lem wit="【大】">姹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丁】">吒</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟<app type="star" corresp="#0604001"><lem wit="【大】">姹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丁】">吒</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱滿馱賀
<lb n="0604a02" ed="T"/>曩賀曩阿<note n="0604002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">密＝蜜【宋】【元】</note><note n="0604002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密【大】，蜜【宋】【元】</note><app n="0604002"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">蜜</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>帝吽發<note n="0604003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吒＋（半音呼）【三】【甲】【乙】，半音【丙】</note><note n="0604003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吒【大】，吒半音呼【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】，吒半音【丙】</note><app n="0604003"><lem wit="【大】">吒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">吒半音呼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">吒<!--CBETA todo type: None-->半音</rdg></app>娑嚩<app type="star" corresp="#0603043"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>賀
<lb n="0604a03" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0603024"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0604a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a0401"><note n="0604004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＋（結）【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，次結【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604004"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">次結</rdg></app>獻<note n="0604005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遏＝閼【三】【乙】【丙】，賢閼【甲】</note><note n="0604005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遏【大】，閼【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】，賢閼【甲】</note><app n="0604005"><lem wit="【大】">遏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">閼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賢閼</rdg></app>伽<note n="0604006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">水＋（印）【丙】</note><note n="0604006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">水【大】，水印【丙】</note><app n="0604006"><lem wit="【大】">水</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">水印</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0604a0406" rend="inline">行者常於壇上。近膝置二
<lb n="0604a05" ed="T"/>淨器。滿盛香水以為<note n="0604007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遏＝閼【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】＊</note><note n="0604007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遏【大】＊，閼【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0604007"><lem wit="【大】">遏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">閼</rdg></app>伽。初迎請時獻右邊
<lb n="0604a06" ed="T"/>者。後奉送時獻左邊者。每奉獻時二羽捧<app type="star" corresp="#0604007"><lem wit="【大】">遏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">閼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0604a07" ed="T"/>伽器。當額奉獻。<note n="0604008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝印【三】【乙】</note><note n="0604008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，印【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604008"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">印</rdg></app>誦真言<note n="0604009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔想〕－【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想【大】，〔－〕【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604009"><lem wit="【大】">想</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>浴本尊及諸
<lb n="0604a08" ed="T"/>聖眾真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0604a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a0901" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娜迦吽</p>
<lb n="0604a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a1001"><note n="0604010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔次結獻蓮花座印〕－【明】【乙】</note><note n="0604010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次結獻蓮華座印【大】，〔－〕【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604010"><lem wit="【大】">次結獻蓮華座印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0604a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a1101">以二羽虛心合掌。以檀慧禪智各頭相著。<note n="0604011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">餘＝飼【丁】</note><note n="0604011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餘【大】，飼【丁】</note><app n="0604011"><lem wit="【大】">餘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">飼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0604a12" ed="T"/>中間六度微屈。頭相離猶如開敷蓮華葉形
<lb n="0604a13" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0604a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a1401" cb:type="dharani">唵迦麼攞娑嚩<note place="inline">二<note n="0604012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【三】【乙】＊</note><note n="0604012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】＊，合引【宋】【元】【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0604012"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">合引</rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0604013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【丁】</note><note n="0604013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【丁】</note><app n="0604013"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0604a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a1501">由結此印真言加持。一切聖眾并及本尊。皆
<lb n="0604a16" ed="T"/>得七寶蓮華為座。</p>
<lb n="0604a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a1701">次結大虛空藏普通供養印。</p>
<lb n="0604a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a1801">以二羽合掌。以戒方二度外縛。以進力反蹙
<lb n="0604a19" ed="T"/>如寶形。結成契已。誦真言四遍。普供養真言
<lb n="0604a20" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0604a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a2101" cb:type="dharani">唵誐誐曩三<note n="0604014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔去〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604014"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>婆<note place="inline">去</note>嚩<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note n="0604015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【三】【乙】【丁】</note><note n="0604015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0604015"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0604a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a2201">想從印出生無量種種供養香花燈燭塗香飲
<lb n="0604a23" ed="T"/>食寶幢幡蓋。即於本尊及一切聖眾前。則成
<lb n="0604a24" ed="T"/>就真實廣大供養。</p>
<lb n="0604a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a2501">次結羯磨印。</p>
<lb n="0604a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604a2601">以<note n="0604016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">止＝二【明】【乙】</note><note n="0604016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止【大】，二【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604016"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">二</rdg></app>羽當心仰掌。以智力<note n="0604017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，〔－〕【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604017"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>捻。反屈力度
<lb n="0604a27" ed="T"/>如寶形。以觀羽仰掌。向前作施願勢結此契
<lb n="0604a28" ed="T"/>已作是思惟。我身即同虛空藏菩薩即誦羯
<lb n="0604a29" ed="T"/>磨真言曰。</p>
<pb n="0604b" xml:id="T20.1146.0604b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0604b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b0101" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛<note n="0604018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">弩＝拏【三】【乙】</note><note n="0604018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">弩【大】，拏【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604018"><lem wit="【大】">弩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">拏</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引鼻聲</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0604b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b0201">由作此觀加持故。行者自身即等同本尊虛
<lb n="0604b03" ed="T"/>空藏菩薩。</p>
<lb n="0604b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b0401">次結三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0604b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b0501"><note n="0604019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即）＋以【三】【乙】</note><note n="0604019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，即以【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604019"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">即以</rdg></app>二羽金剛縛。進力反蹙如寶形。禪智並竪
<lb n="0604b06" ed="T"/>置於當心。即誦三昧耶真言<note n="0604020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔七遍真言〕－【甲】【丁】</note><note n="0604020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七遍真言【大】，〔－〕【甲】【丁】</note><app n="0604020"><lem wit="【大】">七遍真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>曰。</p>
<lb n="0604b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b0701" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0604b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b0801">即<note n="0604021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取＝以【明】【乙】</note><note n="0604021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，以【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604021"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">以</rdg></app>水精念珠安於掌中。合掌當心。誦加持
<lb n="0604b09" ed="T"/>念珠真言三遍真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0604b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b1001" cb:type="dharani">唵尾嚧<note place="inline">引</note>左曩麼攞娑嚩<note place="inline">二<app type="star" corresp="#0604012"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">合引</rdg></app></note>賀<app type="star" corresp="#0603024"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0604b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b1101"><note n="0604022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">則＝即【明】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0604022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】，即【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0604022"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">即</rdg></app>捧珠安於頂上。發是願言。十方世界所有
<lb n="0604b12" ed="T"/>修真言行者。彼所受持一切真言。願速成就。
<lb n="0604b13" ed="T"/>即止羽承珠。觀羽當心。移珠不緩不急。心離
<lb n="0604b14" ed="T"/>散亂。或千或百限數畢已。捧珠頂戴又發是
<lb n="0604b15" ed="T"/>願。一切有情所希望。<note n="0604023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＋（間）【丙】，〔出世〕－【丁】</note><note n="0604023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世出世【大】，世【丁】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->世＋（間）【丙】</note><app n="0604023"><lem wit="【大】">世出世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">世</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">世間出世</rdg></app>間殊勝果報。
<lb n="0604b16" ed="T"/>以我念誦福力。速令成就。即安珠於本處。復
<lb n="0604b17" ed="T"/>結本尊三昧耶印。誦三昧耶真言七遍。頂上
<lb n="0604b18" ed="T"/>散印。又結普供養印誦普<note n="0604024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔通〕－【三】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">通【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604024"><lem wit="【大】">通</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>供養真言七遍。
<lb n="0604b19" ed="T"/>頂上散<note n="0604025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即【三】【乙】，印＋（即）【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0604025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，即【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，印即【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0604025"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">即</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">印即</rdg></app>誦虛空藏菩薩讚歎曰。</p>
<lb n="0604b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b2001" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>素<note n="0604026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＋（聲）【明】【乙】，〔上〕－【丁】</note><note n="0604026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，上聲【明】【乙】，〔－〕【丁】</note><app n="0604026"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><note place="inline">上聲</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0604027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引一）【甲】【乙】，（引）【丁】</note><note n="0604027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合引一【甲】【乙】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->合引【丁】</note><app n="0604027"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">合引一</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">合引</rdg></app></note>囉
<lb n="0604b21" ed="T"/>他<note place="inline">二<note n="0604028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【三】【甲】【乙】【丁】</note><note n="0604028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合引【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0604028"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丁】">合引</rdg></app><note n="0604029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604029"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>迦<note n="0604030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】＊</note><note n="0604030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0604030"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>捨摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>麼<note n="0604031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">柅＝抳【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0604031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">柅【大】，抳【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0604031"><lem wit="【大】">柅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">抳</rdg></app><note n="0604032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（二合）＋二【宋】【元】，二＋（合引）【明】【乙】，二＝合【甲】，二＋（合）【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0604032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，二合二【宋】【元】，二合引【明】【乙】，合【甲】，二合【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0604032"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><note place="inline">二合二</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">合</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】"><note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0604b22" ed="T"/>阿<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0603028"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>捨<note n="0604033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00754"/>＝孽【三】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0604033" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00754"/>【大】＊，孽【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0604033"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB00754"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">孽</rdg></app>婆<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0603028"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">去聲</rdg></app></note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0603015"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">荼</rdg></app><note n="0604034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">馱＝馳【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】，〔馱夜反三〕－【丁】</note><note n="0604034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">馱夜反三【大】，〔－〕【丁】，馳夜反三【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0604034"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">馱夜<note n="0604035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】【乙】</note><note n="0604035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反【大】，切【明】【乙】</note><app n="0604035"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">切</rdg></app><note n="0604036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【甲】</note><note n="0604036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，二【甲】</note><app n="0604036"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】"><note place="inline">馳夜反三</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0604b23" ed="T"/>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0604033"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB00754"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">孽</rdg></app>婆<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0603028"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">去聲</rdg></app></note>曩謨<app type="star" corresp="#0604030"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>窣<note n="0604037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">堵＝𤌄【甲】</note><note n="0604037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">堵【大】，𤌄【甲】</note><app n="0604037"><lem wit="【大】">堵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">𤌄</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note n="0604038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔四〕－【丁】</note><note n="0604038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四【大】，〔－〕【丁】</note><app n="0604038"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0604b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b2401">誦讚歎已。即取左邊閼伽。當額奉獻。即結
<lb n="0604b25" ed="T"/>前軍吒利印。<note n="0604039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左＝右【丁】</note><note n="0604039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">左【大】，右【丁】</note><app n="0604039"><lem wit="【大】">左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">右</rdg></app>旋一匝解界。次結三昧耶
<lb n="0604b26" ed="T"/>印。奉送一切聖眾。奉送真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0604b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b2701" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>穆</p>
<lb n="0604b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0604b2801">舉印安頂上。誦真言七遍。即成奉送一切聖
<lb n="0604b29" ed="T"/>眾。復結三部心三昧<note n="0604040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＋（印）【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0604040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，耶印【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0604040"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">耶印</rdg></app>各誦三遍。次結護身
<pb n="0604c" xml:id="T20.1146.0604c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0604c01" ed="T"/>印。如前印於五處。即禮佛發願隨意出道場。
<lb n="0604c02" ed="T"/>轉讀大乘印佛印塔。廣行檀施常須饒益一
<lb n="0604c03" ed="T"/>切有情。</p>
<lb n="0604c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>大虛空藏菩薩念誦<note n="0604041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（儀軌）＋法【甲】【丁】，甲本奧書曰，久安四年戊辰七月一日以成蓮院之阿闍梨御房之御本書之實範，七月二十日奉傳受，乙本奧書曰，貞享三年九月十七夜點之又以高麗印本及本朝所傳本校正之河南延命沙門淨嚴四十有八，元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊敬，丙本奧書曰，依三十帖本改直之慙記，依成身院御經藏本交點了治承二戊戌六月二十七日以御本加青點了玄胤</note><note n="0604041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，儀軌法【甲】【丁】，甲本奧書曰，久安四年戊辰七月一日以成蓮院之阿闍梨御房之御本書之實範，七月二十日奉傳受，乙本奧書曰，貞享三年九月十七夜點之又以高麗印本及本朝所傳本校正之河南延命沙門淨嚴四十有八，元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊敬，丙本奧書曰，依三十帖本改直之慙記，依成身院御經藏本交點了治承二戊戌六月二十七日以御本加青點了玄胤</note><app n="0604041"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丁】">儀軌法</rdg></app><note n="0604041" type="rest" place="foot">甲本奧書曰，久安四年戊辰七月一日以成蓮院之阿闍梨御房之御本書之實範，七月二十日奉傳受，乙本奧書曰，貞享三年九月十七夜點之又以高麗印本及本朝所傳本校正之河南延命沙門淨嚴四十有八，元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊敬，丙本奧書曰，依三十帖本改直之慙記，依成身院御經藏本交點了治承二戊戌六月二十七日以御本加青點了玄胤</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
